					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">In-game, the timing of the play routine, particularly with respect to whether a write hits before or after the period divider resets, may depend on the CPU load of the game logic. Sound effects also end up changing the channels' relative phase</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

